analysis is proprietary and has its own licensing terms. If you use the 
original CGSS data:

- You must register with the CGSS data provider (http://www.chinagss.org)
- You must agree to the CGSS data use agreement
- You must cite CGSS in any publications

The synthetic data provided in this repository (synthetic_data_generator.R) 
is generated artificially and is free to use and distribute.

